{"tid":1950011,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】進度匯報 + 需要大家幫忙 #認同 #所以幫李伯盧開post #政事","createTime":"2020-03-30T05:07:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-30T05:15:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8ab8a90435504ec85ead1e514c90ef56175d9193","tid":1950011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:07:31.000Z","msg":"#認同 #所以幫李伯盧開post #政事<br />\n<br />\n【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】進度匯報 + 需要大家幫忙<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1940299\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1940299</a><br />\n<br />\n呢個Post主要係俾一直有留意開【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】嘅手足睇。<br />\n<br />\n首先，匯報一下進度，聯署人數突破左一千：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jOHr5WP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjOHr5WP.png&h=b1da11d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係一個好嘅開始，但人數上，離俾到候選人壓力嘅程度，仲係差好遠<br />\n<br />\n所以我呢度有四點，希望各位支持嘅手足幫幫忙，令我地儘快收集到最多聯署：<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">1）希望大家可以連登度開新Post推銷個聯署，推上熱門</span></span></strong><br />\n一來小弟受P牌所限，無法自己推Post，到而家都未能推上熱門<br />\n二來人多勢眾，多D人開新Post講個聯署，聲勢都強D<br />\n基本上個Post有以下幾樣野就得：<br />\n<br />\n（FB Link：）<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/legcopetition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Flegcopetition&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=cf78468f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/legcopetition</a><br />\n（聯署link：）<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf--3WrL03pxfJALAgIAMIarSqyBNrbfTYFVZaxafm8wmt23Q/viewform?usp=sf_link\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSf--3WrL03pxfJALAgIAMIarSqyBNrbfTYFVZaxafm8wmt23Q%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dsf_link&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=52ca584f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSf--3WrL03pxfJALAgIAMIarSqyBNrbfTYFVZaxafm8wmt23Q/viewform?usp=sf_link</a><br />\n（或簡短版聯署link：）<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/ZgA6UiEXDMW43x3A9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FZgA6UiEXDMW43x3A9&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=ea7e14e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/ZgA6UiEXDMW43x3A9</a><br />\n<br />\n（同聯署嘅三點：）<br />\n呼籲香港選民，於2020年立法會選舉，不投票給以下三種參選人：<br />\n（1）反對舉行初選/協調的，不投！<br />\n（2）有初選/協調機制但不參與的，不投！<br />\n（3）初選落選後不肯退選或協調組隊的，不投！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">2）希望大家可以去Like個聯署facebook Page</span></span></strong><br />\n（FB Link：）<br />\n<a href=\"http://fb.me/legcopetition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Flegcopetition&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=cf78468f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">fb.me/legcopetition</a><br />\n而家聯署人數過千，聯署facebook page都只係100個Like左右，唔成比例<br />\n好容易俾人話聯署有灌水之嫌（雖然我知道唔係）<br />\n個facebook page多Like會有助聯署嘅公信力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3）希望大家可以到連登外宣揚開去</span></strong></span><br />\n我地聯署要宣傳嘅唔止係連登手足們，而係所有民主派選民<br />\n希望大家到whatsapp group，Facebook，Twitter，Reddit，telegram，Instagram.....<br />\n可以share嘅地方都share<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4）希望大家可以盡量指出聯署可以改進嘅地方</span></strong></span><br />\n小弟第一次整聯署，好多野都係邊做邊學<br />\n已經有好多comment幫到我改左好多野<br />\n大家有建議希望盡量提出<br />\n改到嘅我改，唔同意嘅我亦會盡量解釋返立場<br />\n<br />\n就係咁多，希望大家努力，一齊爭取35+，議會過半！"},{"pid":"df7dc25ef12358ce7101d01b96535e65fe10e155","tid":1950011,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:11:26.000Z","msg":"聯署：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/LHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FLHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=f8b12619\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/LHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA</a><br />\nFB： <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/legcopetition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flegcopetition&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=7cd52cd2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/legcopetition</a><br />\nTG： <a href=\"http://t.me/legcopetition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flegcopetition&d=HeGJypC3zV9uypmZg8TJ2UBBI%2BG%2BtQAW9Loz3QxUp%2BM%3D&h=e889e1d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/legcopetition</a><br />\n<br />\n大家Share開去！"},{"pid":"78e24e325bfbf5f017f466df2f16f1d7ba8b06fb","tid":1950011,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:12:16.000Z","msg":"唔該曬樓主開Post加持！！！！<br />\n<br />\n感激不盡！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d182fc848b59a5219f43eac28506254c3d92b560","tid":1950011,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T05:15:08.000Z","msg":"大家認同嘅， 請都幫手開post支持同推廣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}